</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="49.[151,1436,260,503]" box="[199,1183,296,323]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,296,323]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Distribution.</emphasis>
Europe; also North Africa. 
<collectingCountry box="[663,762,297,323]" name="Portugal" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Portugal</collectingCountry>
: three provinces, all over the country.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="49.[151,1436,260,503]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,300,333,359]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Ecology.</emphasis>
Recorded in 
<collectingCountry box="[446,541,333,359]" name="Portugal" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Portugal</collectingCountry>
from a brackish marshland, a dry deciduous forest and orchards. In northwestern Europe, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hydrophorinae" baseAuthorityName="Haliday" baseAuthorityYear="1851" box="[245,365,369,395]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Schoenophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="versutus">
<emphasis box="[245,365,369,395]" italics="true" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">S. versutus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
seems to prefer open marshlands, primarily in the coastal region and often on sandy soils (
<bibRefCitation author="Pollet, M." pageId="49" pageNumber="50" pagination="1 - 190" refId="ref34362" refString="Pollet, M. (2000) A documented Red List of the dolichopodid flies (Diptera: Dolichopodidae) of Flanders [in Dutch with English summary]. Communications of the Institute of Nature Conservation, 8, 1 - 190." type="journal article" year="2000">Pollet 2000</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="49.[151,1436,260,503]" box="[199,646,440,467]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,337,440,467]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Rarity (%).</emphasis>
4.6 (rare). Fairly rare (FL).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="49.[151,1436,260,503]" box="[199,654,476,503]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,386,476,503]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Activity period.</emphasis>
